Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.97,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(364,361)}Murder Intent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}it went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, it went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done what you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T, {\alpha&HFF&}that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have received all the messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have one thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? {\alpha&HFF&}An email?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? An email?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she wants to meet you she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! {\alpha&HFF&}That's to say that Mikami has confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's to say that Mikami has confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do now is to wait for Near to request a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, {\alpha&HFF&}this is my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have predicted how you are going to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gevanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, I have checked the notebook and confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami has written down a page per day for the last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The names on them match the victims. And Mikami has not acted any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. {\alpha&HFF&}Well then, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Well then, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to show you regarding the Kira Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't I regarded as Kira by you? {\alpha&HFF&}If so, you wouldn't want to reveal what you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't I regarded as Kira by you? If so, you wouldn't want to reveal what you look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to reveal my face to show you what I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, by revealing my face, I can reveal something to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we will be able to put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to put an end to this wrong idea you have of me quickly as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near is doing this to show that Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light is Kira, he will be doing this to kill Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before that, I would like to make an agreement with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just spell out whatever requests you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, all members from each team are to attend this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning, we will gather everyone who is after Kira at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my side, it will be like I told you. Four people including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will make up the whole SPK team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for the abducted Mr. Mogi, we will bring him along, while releasing Amane without revealing where we are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can confirm our release of Amane before moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near. {\alpha&HFF&}Roger that. With me included, we have a team of five over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near. Roger that. {\alpha&HFF&}With me included, we have a team of five over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near. Roger that. With me included, we have a team of five over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}with Mogi with you, I have only three other people with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... with Mogi with you, I have only three other people with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. {\alpha&HFF&}Well then, next will be deciding our meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Well then, next will be deciding our meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Daikoku Wharf at the Southeast area. At the moment, it is not being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a place also known as "Yellow Box".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is good enough, we will proceed with the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that, Yagami Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, you should be able to do what you want to do as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing. I would like someone in the investigation team to bring the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of you came over to meet me, there will be no one keeping guard on the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can promise you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not attempt to take the notebook away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To confirm that you are bringing the real one, and are indeed from the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will just need Mr. Aizawa's confirmation, and I will believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, please make sure someone other than L is carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think that L is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, {\alpha&HFF&}but I will get to choose who carries it. Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, but I will get to choose who carries it. {\alpha&HFF&}Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, but I will get to choose who carries it. Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we are only left with the day and date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day and date? Time is the important factor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mikami is doing his judgment from midnight, {\alpha&HFF&}he must have picked out his targets during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mikami is doing his judgment from midnight, he must have picked out his targets during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take this time into consideration...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 days after today, on the 28th, at 1pm. How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1pm? {\alpha&HFF&}That's the time I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1pm? That's the time I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near knows how Mikami work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. On our side, any time is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, 3 days later at 1pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have predicted and read your moves. I am definitely going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am quite busy today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you're not staying until the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands will be full over the next 2 to 3 days with police work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami and Takada have already been instructed on what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last instruction to kill Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke? There's an attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting away! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, let's get into NHN quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that! With this kind of attack, it will be dangerous inside NHN!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, it's better to get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, please get on the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the bike and get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A team and B team, stay around Takada-sama. Other teams, please go after the attacker in the car just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh, I have confirmed her safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help Takada-sama into the number 7 car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be...! Takada-sama is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you hit Takada-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the attackers is armed with various weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takada Guard Team and the police are doing their best to find out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Near again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}He had arranged for us to meet in 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... He had arranged for us to meet in 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will he gain from something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, rather than saying Near is behind this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys have been waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many guards does Takada have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Since when is Japanese allowed to have possessions of those nice arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, you want to know where my accomplice has taken Takada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly fire at--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot. It's not like you were going to tell us a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going against Kira-sama is definitely a crime punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person... {\alpha&HFF&}is one of the people Yagami-kun told me to be especially careful of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person... is one of the people Yagami-kun told me to be especially careful of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! {\alpha&HFF&}Mihael Keehl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! Mihael Keehl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off everything you are wearing and put them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, this time, the abduction of Takada has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? {\alpha&HFF&}If that's the case, Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? If that's the case, Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To tell you the truth, the guard that I sent has already confirmed it was done by Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the trouble my guard has caused, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, if it's you, can you get through to Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I do have a way to do that, Mello will not respond at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I take off my underwear, can you pass me the blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guard Team has taken down one of the accomplices of the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are currently still tracking where Takada-sama is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it was no use after all, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}Takada-san's phone is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Takada-san's phone is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With no way to get in contact with Takada, there's nothing other to do than to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other way than this. {\alpha&HFF&}I have to be the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other way than this. I have to be the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The identity of the man who was shot to death is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matt... {\alpha&HFF&}I got you killed... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matt... I got you killed... {\alpha&HFF&}sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matt... I got you killed... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can contact me through her phone, that would mean... {\alpha&HFF&}she's gotten away from Mello... or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can contact me through her phone, that would mean... she's gotten away from Mello... {\alpha&HFF&}or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can contact me through her phone, that would mean... she's gotten away from Mello... or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun! {\alpha&HFF&}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now. Calm down and answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the place. {\alpha&HFF&}Do you know where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, the place. Do you know where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am locked inside a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were at the expressway, I did saw a signboard stating "Nagano". {\alpha&HFF&}Right now, we're in some building...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were at the expressway, I did saw a signboard stating "Nagano". Right now, we're in some building...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san. {\alpha&HFF&}You're Kira's spokeswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san. You're Kira's spokeswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember I told you the possibility that your life would be in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those situations, {\alpha&HFF&}I told you what you are supposed to do. Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those situations, I told you what you are supposed to do. {\alpha&HFF&}Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those situations, I told you what you are supposed to do. Do you remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The things that Yagami-kun told me to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I was stripped naked, I did not resist, but did what Yagami-kun said, and placed staying alive as my top priority...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun, I have done everything you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, {\alpha&HFF&}you know what to do from now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, you know what to do from now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do as much judgment as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, {\alpha&HFF&}but Yagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but Yagami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa-san, Ide-san, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san will stay watch in HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as much judgment as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... {\alpha&HFF&}yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes... {\alpha&HFF&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she is telling me this, means that she has taken out the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, she must be in a state where she can't move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakajima-kun, I am going to the actual scene of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step on it. I've gotten her location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the freeway and head towards Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's Karuizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... that will take at least 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mello, and we don't know what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. {\alpha&HFF&}Aizawa and Ide are still too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. Aizawa and Ide are still too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just sat in the frontseats without me asking them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, I don't even have to do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi, {\alpha&HFF&}suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi, suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On 26th January 2013, at 2:32pm, {\alpha&HFF&}burnt all her belongings and anything written down before burning herself to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On 26th January 2013, at 2:32pm, burnt all her belongings and anything written down before burning herself to death.
